{"tid":1965284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇見過/經歷過香港黑社會？","createTime":"2020-04-09T11:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T14:49:26.000Z","uid":170044,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ebae4df19d653cb48b4c231614c8dae91bb41be7","tid":1965284,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"香港黑社會問題不嬲嚴重<br />\n雖然好多移民晒去荷蘭<br />\n大家可唔可以分享下見識過咩黑社會場面?<br />\n收保護費 打交 劈友呢啲<br />\n成日聽人講元朗開得酒吧9成都有背景<br />\n721 831呢啲基本嘢唔洗講<br />\n但想了解多啲香港黑社會<br />\n點解尖沙咀咁可以雜過油麻地旺角<br />\n去親山林道同尖東都驚 係咪近酒吧"},{"pid":"aead0fe33dee741506ecdad4eb27db7b30bd8468","tid":1965284,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"Cctoy"},{"pid":"29e7bf2cdf7b4656cba92a108b7cc09810910d3c","tid":1965284,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"識個老細同九指華一齊做野<br />\n你話佢係咪黑社會啦"},{"pid":"2aa8154992f2b8ef61ae3fc88c6d9a471b7384b2","tid":1965284,"uid":56698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"啲老黑大佬好有禮貌，我依啲做細嘅見到都唔好意思<br />\n真係黑警恐怖啲"},{"pid":"2a4d9e866b115ffda7e3572956ef16aecfe98a49","tid":1965284,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"一街陳浩南打扮mk仔企老翻檔睇水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365611cc8a6c9399fff3c29094c36146e6def4fd","tid":1965284,"uid":5971,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2aa8154992f2b8ef61ae3fc88c6d9a471b7384b2","tid":1965284,"uid":56698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"啲老黑大佬好有禮貌，我依啲做細嘅見到都唔好意思<br />\n真係黑警恐怖啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"試過見到黑社會做野<br />\n<br />\n通常好有隊形<br />\n<br />\n有一個人拎大聲公講野<br />\n<br />\n指揮啲伙記<br />\n<br />\n其餘就跟order做野<br />\n<br />\n題外話：早幾日見到有前議員拎大聲公講野都俾人告<br />\n<br />\n我打算都試下告佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c210f071611ff64c4ef8bae9fe3307a191a3472","tid":1965284,"uid":134087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"佔旺都見夠啦"},{"pid":"5935ca75bb8b6b9f040efddf5d07f85d35437083","tid":1965284,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"小學生時代見過一群人拎住刀追另一群人<br />\n<br />\n唔知係唔係黑社會<br />\n<br />\n只記得當時睇得好興奮"},{"pid":"744dc21723d1f77ea1b919fb058b509bcb87e4c2","tid":1965284,"uid":259532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"909db70503299db1cefd4fa9d4d04e8e02a58cc7","tid":1965284,"uid":87283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"初中時期見過一個阿叔係啲叔父嘅跟班打手。見過佢出手好兇狠。<br />\n<br />\n期後喺我AL嗰陣見到佢入嚟學校做校工。好好笑容～同班師弟好friend一齊打波。又好take care啲後生。<br />\n<br />\n感覺幾奇妙～"},{"pid":"32ce6eb83df16a895df97f23a9992a89651d869f","tid":1965284,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a4d9e866b115ffda7e3572956ef16aecfe98a49","tid":1965284,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"一街陳浩南打扮mk仔企老翻檔睇水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"20年前嘅黑社會，仲要有嗰係舖頭對面望實啲人有冇俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc23b3b98c166931aef2c8ad8b5c8524b11c69da","tid":1965284,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"香港黑社會唔洗驚架喎<br />\n廢廢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338d03915f885fdaa5dc74bf8e93ec5aee9f55a4","tid":1965284,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa8154992f2b8ef61ae3fc88c6d9a471b7384b2","tid":1965284,"uid":56698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"cite